# This directory stores technology decision logs.
#
# Decision Log files document technology choices made for projects,
# including rationale, tradeoff analysis, and implementation costs.
#
# Format: YYYY-MM-DD-project-name.md
# Example: 2026-04-22-jis-handbook-checker.md
#
# Each file should include "Technology Selected: [technology name]"
# for consistency checking in session end hooks.
